Description: Tula Soft Nappa Gold Leather Small Clutch Bag 8905 This soft nappa crossbody bag is part of the party bags range by Tula, the ideal accessory for evenings functions or weddings. Made from soft nappa leather it features a front press stud popper fastening and Tula branding. One main compartment with a handy back wall zipped pocket. One slip - in pocket underneath the front flap and a zipped pocket on the back of the bag. Pink internal lining in cotton cloth. The shoulder strap is detachable and can therefore be used as a small clutch.
